"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417536","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-09-17","<p>There is no record of this letter having been received by my Department. If the hon. Member will forward a copy I shall ensure it is actioned as a matter of urgency.</p><p> </p>","Grantham and Stamford","Nick Boles","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417536/answer",,,,,,"2015-09-17T09:46:02.523Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417536/answer","Biography information for Nick Boles","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417536/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-09-08","Members: Correspondence","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, when he plans to respond to the letter from the hon. Member for Ashfield the Shadow Business Secretary on women executives on company boards dated 15 June 2015.","false","Biography information for Gloria De Piero","Ashfield","Gloria De Piero","9636"
